---
import Layout from '../../layouts/LayoutEN.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cookies Policy - Omar Fuentes" description="Cookies Policy for Omar Fuentes website. Information about cookies and tracking technologies used in compliance with U.S. regulations.">
  
  <main class="pt-24 pb-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12">
      
      <header class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-black mb-4">Cookies Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-black">Last updated: January 28, 2026</p>
      </header>

      <!-- 1. What Are Cookies -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">1. What Are Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8 mb-6">
          Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device (computer, tablet, or mobile) when you visit a website.
          They help the website remember information about your visit, which can make it easier to visit the site again
          and make the site more useful to you.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8">
          At <span class="font-semibold text-black">Omar Fuentes</span>, we use cookies to enhance your experience
          on our website and to analyze how our site is used.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- 2. How We Use Cookies -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">2. How We Use Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8 mb-4">We use cookies for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-gray-700 list-disc">
          <li><span class="font-semibold text-black">Essential Cookies:</span> Required for the website to function properly</li>
          <li><span class="font-semibold text-black">Performance Cookies:</span> Help us understand how visitors interact with our site</li>
          <li><span class="font-semibold text-black">Functional Cookies:</span> Remember your preferences and settings</li>
          <li><span class="font-semibold text-black">Marketing Cookies:</span> Used to deliver relevant advertisements</li>
          <li><span class="font-semibold text-black">Analytics Cookies:</span> Help us analyze website traffic and usage</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- 3. Types of Cookies We Use -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">3. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">3.1 Essential Cookies</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8 mb-4">These cookies are necessary for the website to function and cannot be switched off:</p>
        <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-gray-700 list-disc">
          <li>Session management</li>
          <li>Security tokens</li>
          <li>Load balancing</li>
          <li>Basic site functionality</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">3.2 Performance Cookies</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8 mb-4">These cookies help us understand how our website is performing:</p>
        <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-gray-700 list-disc">
          <li>Page load times</li>
          <li>Error reporting</li>
          <li>Response times</li>
          <li>Site performance metrics</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">3.3 Analytics Cookies</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8 mb-4">These cookies help us analyze website traffic and usage:</p>
        <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-gray-700 list-disc">
          <li>Google Analytics</li>
          <li>Visitor behavior tracking</li>
          <li>Popular pages identification</li>
          <li>Traffic sources analysis</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">3.4 Marketing Cookies</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8 mb-4">These cookies are used for marketing purposes:</p>
        <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-gray-700 list-disc">
          <li>Ad personalization</li>
          <li>Campaign tracking</li>
          <li>Conversion tracking</li>
          <li>Remarketing</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- 4. Third-Party Cookies -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">4. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8 mb-4">
          We use third-party services that may place cookies on your device:
        </p>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-6">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Google Analytics</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Used for website analytics and user behavior tracking</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Google Ads and Google AdSense</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Used for advertising, ad personalization, ad frequency capping, conversion tracking, and ad performance measurement</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mt-2">
                You can manage Google ad personalization at{" "}
                <a class="font-semibold hover:underline" href="https://adssettings.google.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Google Ads Settings</a>.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">Meta (Facebook/Instagram)</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Used for social media marketing and analytics</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-black mb-2">LinkedIn</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Used for professional networking and marketing</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 5. Managing Cookies -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">5. Managing Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8 mb-4">You can control and manage cookies in several ways:</p>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">5.1 Browser Settings</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8 mb-4">Most browsers allow you to:</p>
        <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-gray-700 list-disc">
          <li>View what cookies are stored</li>
          <li>Delete existing cookies</li>
          <li>Block third-party cookies</li>
          <li>Block cookies from specific sites</li>
          <li>Disable all cookies</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">5.2 Cookie Consent Banner</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8 mb-4">
          Our website uses a cookie consent banner that allows you to accept or reject.
        </p>
        <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-gray-700 list-disc">
          <li>If you accept, we may enable personalized ads</li>
          <li>If you reject, we’ll show non-personalized ads</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8 mt-4">
          You can change your choice by deleting the site cookies (or local storage) in your browser and reloading the page to see the banner again.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- 6. Cookie Duration -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">6. Cookie Duration</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8 mb-4">Different cookies have different lifespans:</p>
        <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-gray-700 list-disc">
          <li><span class="font-semibold text-black">Session Cookies:</span> Deleted when you close your browser</li>
          <li><span class="font-semibold text-black">Persistent Cookies:</span> Remain on your device for a set period</li>
          <li><span class="font-semibold text-black">Analytics Cookies:</span> Typically 2 years</li>
          <li><span class="font-semibold text-black">Marketing Cookies:</span> Typically 30 days to 1 year</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- 7. Your Rights (CCPA Compliance) -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">7. Your Rights (CCPA Compliance)</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8 mb-4">
          Under the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA), you have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-gray-700 list-disc">
          <li>Know what personal information is collected</li>
          <li>Delete personal information collected through cookies</li>
          <li>Opt-out of the sale of personal information</li>
          <li>Non-discrimination for exercising privacy rights</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8">
          To exercise these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@omarfuentes.com" class="text-primary-blue hover:underline">contact@omarfuentes.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- 8. International Data Transfers -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">8. International Data Transfers</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8 mb-4">
          Some cookies may transfer data to countries outside the United States:
        </p>
        <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-gray-700 list-disc">
          <li>Google services may process data in various countries</li>
          <li>Social media platforms may transfer data internationally</li>
          <li>We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place</li>
          <li>All transfers comply with applicable privacy laws</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- 9. Do Not Track -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">9. Do Not Track</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8 mb-4">
          Our website currently does not respond to Do Not Track (DNT) signals. However, you can:
        </p>
        <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-gray-700 list-disc">
          <li>Use browser settings to block tracking cookies</li>
          <li>Opt out of advertising through industry programs</li>
          <li>Contact us directly to opt out of tracking</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- 10. Updates to This Policy -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">10. Updates to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8 mb-4">
          We may update this Cookies Policy from time to time to reflect changes in:
        </p>
        <ul class="grid gap-2 pl-6 text-gray-700 list-disc">
          <li>The cookies we use</li>
          <li>How we use cookies</li>
          <li>Legal requirements</li>
          <li>Industry best practices</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8">
          The "Last updated" date at the top of this page indicates when this policy was last modified.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- 11. Contact Information -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">11. Contact Information</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-8 mb-4">
          If you have questions about our use of cookies or this policy, please contact us:
        </p>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 p-6">
          <div class="grid gap-2 text-gray-700">
            <p>
              <span class="font-semibold text-black">Business:</span> Omar Fuentes
            </p>
            <p>
              <span class="font-semibold text-black">Service Area:</span> United States
            </p>
            <p>
              <span class="font-semibold text-black">Phone:</span> +57 310 785 1074
            </p>
            <p>
              <span class="font-semibold text-black">Email:</span> <a href="mailto:contact@omarfuentes.com" class="text-primary-blue hover:underline">contact@omarfuentes.com</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
